data.description: Beautiful meticulously maintained single level home on .39 acres! Built in 2016,1805sqft, 3 bedrooms, 2 baths and office/den. New LVP flooring throughout main living areas, open concept floor plan with vaulted ceilings and big windows to let in natural light. Well appointed kitchen has a breakfast bar island, stainless steel appliances and spacious walk-in pantry. Comfortable living room boasts a rock gas fireplace and mantle. Huge main suite with a walk-in closet and bathroom with dual vanities and new shower. Enjoy amazing outdoor living with views of Rathdrum mountain from the covered patio with built in lights and sun shades that opens to a large level yard. 3 car garage and RV parking behind double gates, sprinkler system front and back, and AC. Located in a cul-de-sac and close to all amenities!
